trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"></xref> and <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"></xref> events.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting"> </xref> och <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting"> </xref> händelser.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that the connection process has begun (for example, a user has selected a control and clicked a connect verb), but is not yet completed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>händelse utlöses av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A>metoden och anger att anslutningen har börjat (till exempel en användare har valt en kontroll och klickar på Anslut verb) men ännu inte har slutförts.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsConnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: Händelsen ger en möjlighet att avbryta en anslutning innan den är klar.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is successfully completed, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected> event.
trans-unit.target: Om anslutningen är slutfört den här händelsen är följt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>händelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnected>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> event is raised by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> method, and it indicates that a user has clicked a disconnect verb, or the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> method has otherwise been called.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>händelse utlöses av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A>metoden och anger att användaren har klickat på ett disconnect-verb eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A>annars metoden har anropats.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.DisconnectWebParts%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnWebPartsDisconnecting%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>

trans-unit.source: The event provides an opportunity to cancel the process of ending a connection before it is complete.
trans-unit.target: Händelsen ger en möjlighet att avbryta processen för att avsluta en anslutning innan den är klar.

trans-unit.source: If the connection is ended successfully, this event is followed by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected> event.
trans-unit.target: Om anslutningen är har uppnått den här händelsen är följt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>händelse.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnected>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs class contains information about the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> events.
trans-unit.target: Klassen WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs innehåller information om den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting>händelser.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsDisconnecting> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartsConnecting>

trans-unit.source: It provides access to the Web Parts controls that are being connected or disconnected.
trans-unit.target: Det ger åtkomst till webbdelar kontroller som ansluten eller frånkopplad.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"></xref> class without a specified connection.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartConnectionsCancelEventArgs"> </xref> klass utan en viss anslutning.
